Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要换换呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也不对头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今天可得卯足了劲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你了
